|designer = Chris Walter (2002)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://archive.cardesignnews.com/autoshows/2003/newyork/highlights/h05-ford-futura.html|title=New York Auto Show 2003 Highlights - Ford Futura|work=cardesignnews.com|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070807235939/http://archive.cardesignnews.com/autoshows/2003/newyork/highlights/h05-ford-futura.html|archivedate=August 7, 2007}}</ref>
