====Model year changes====
1981 &ndash; All-new model &ndash; the Escort was a world car. Original trims were Base, L, GL, GLX and SS. [[Mercury Lynx]] is Escort's twin.

1982 &ndash; The GT replaced the SS. There were now new trims as the Base, L, GL, GLX and GT.

